data.description: Located in beautiful East Escondido, this home sits on a large corner lot and enjoys mountain views. Spacious floorplan with a bright kitchen boasting stainless steel appliances, vaulted ceiliings in LR, wood laminate and tile flooring throughout. All 4 bedrooms upstairs along with a large laundry room. Primary bath has 2 closets.Backyard hosts a planter area,fruit vines and dog run.No neighbors behind.Sunrun Solar w/battery backup leased. NO HOA or Mello-roos. Close to Lake Dixon and Daley Ranch and neighborhood park.Buyer to assume lease for Sunrun Solar lease. Docs attached under Docs tab. In accordance with FHA guidelines Buyer letters will not be submitted to Seller.
